title: Know what`s Kris Jenner`s most embarrassing moment with ex-Bruce
text: Know what`s Kris Jenner`s most embarrassing moment with ex-Bruce Monday, 12 October 2015 (15 minutes ago) *Washington D.C., Oct. 10(ANI): Kris Jenner recently opened up about her most embarrassing moment and it takes us back in the time when she was married to Bruce Jenner, who is now know as Caitlyn Jenner after transition.* Washington D.C., Oct. 10(ANI): Kris Jenner recently opened up about her most embarrassing moment and it takes us back in the time when she was married to Bruce Jenner, who is now know as Caitlyn Jenner after transition. The 59-year-old TV personality said that the most embarrassing moment for her was when she was with the 65-year-old reality star on a commercial airliner in first class, reports E! Online. The 'Keeping Up With the Kardashians' star added that the duo had sex in the bathroom and when they came out nobody said anything, but later a flight attendant made an announcement, "Congratulations, Mr. and Mrs. Jenner! You've just joined the mile-high club. We're so proud of you, and we decided to give you a bottle of champagne! Yay!" Jenner said that she was mortified by this incident. (ANI)
